					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eric-h" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(474585); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=474585&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610182957" alt="eric_h" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=474585)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eric-h" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(474585); return false;" >eric_h</a></span> <span class="odate time_1313772294 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">19 Aug 2011 16:44</span>
