			<div class="content" id="post-content-1234071">
									

<p>Here is Junior, the reality-bending cat!</p>
<p>I am well-aware this is an awful concept for an SCP, and everyone would tell me &quot;For the love of God, don't write that!&quot; if I had asked. This is pretty much the idea of the challenge&#8230;combining two Cliche List items at random is not going to get you a good concept.</p>
<p>His story: He has some interesting powers, but they're limited, because he's no smarter than an average cat, and just wants normal cat things. Out of character, I didn't want this to turn out as &quot;<a href="/scp-239">SCP-239</a>, only it's a cat.&quot;</p>

