<p>[Use of SCP-795 to terminate recalcitrant D-Class personnel approved. – O5-4]</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This rubs me the wrong way. I'm not sure if that's just my knee-jerk response to Humorous Addenda or not. But it seems a little <em>too</em> silly.</p>

